A vibrant Studio Ghibli style illustration of a fantastical theme park at golden hour, featuring whimsical dinosaurs peeking through lush jungle foliage beside an Egyptian pyramid, a medieval castle with dragon-shaped roller coaster tracks winding through the sky, and a futuristic silver spaceship area in the distance. In the foreground, a family of silhouettes stands in wonder, gazing at the magical landscape. The scene is bathed in warm orange and soft purple sunset hues, with fireflies and gentle steam rising from water attractions. Sweeping curved pathways connect the distinct themed zones like flowing rivers, and cherry blossom petals drift through the air, adding dreamlike wonder to this celebration of adventure and imagination.
